npc.dialogs.Andre_0: <%s> Hello kiddo, I hope you are doing well.
npc.dialogs.Andre_1: <%s> Howdy, kiddo.  Searching for animal care supplies?  I’ve got 'em right here.
npc.dialogs.Bernina_0: <%s> Have you heard of the Elna fashion brand? My sister started that company!
npc.dialogs.Bernina_1: <%s> Hmmm, it looks like a new hat would be just the thing to brighten up your day!
npc.dialogs.Elna_0: <%s> Hello %s! Care to try out some new looks today?
npc.dialogs.Elna_1: <%s> It would be amazing if we could have coordinated outfits for all the people in the settlement!
npc.dialogs.Fenny_1: <%s> I just came out with a new plushie design today!  I hope you'll look forward to it whenever it goes on sale!
npc.dialogs.Harley:_0: <%s> Come get some arts and crafts to spread holiday cheer!
npc.dialogs.Harley:_1: <%s> I really should practice my drums some more…
npc.dialogs.Harley_0: <%s> Come get some arts and crafts to spread holiday cheer!
npc.dialogs.Harley_1: <%s> I really should practice my drums some more…
npc.dialogs.Jess_0: <%s> The welcome center is getting more and more cozy everyday!  I love the updates you made to the place!
npc.dialogs.Jess_3: <%s> Aha! I just thought of another angle to advertise the Adventurer's Settlement Package!
npc.dialogs.Laly_0: <%s> Oooo do you have any minerals? I would love to process some for you!
npc.dialogs.Langley_0: <%s> Oh don't mind the smoke! I got everything under control!
npc.dialogs.Langley_1: <%s> ... ... Oh hi %s, I was deep in thought there haha.
npc.dialogs.Matan:_0: <%s> I've completed a new work today!  Would you like to purchase a copy of it?
npc.dialogs.Matan:_1: <%s> Is there anything in my collection that piques your fancy?
npc.dialogs.Matan_0: <%s> I've completed a new work today!  Would you like to purchase a copy of it?
npc.dialogs.Matan_1: <%s> Is there anything in my collection that piques your fancy?
npc.dialogs.Pamela_0: <%s> Hello %s, have you discovered any interesting dishes recently?
npc.dialogs.Pamela_1: <%s> I wonder if my children back home would enjoy pork carrot wontons? Oh hello %s, how have you been?
npc.dialogs.Pamela_2: <%s> The place you've built for me is amazing! I love being able to cook while on my holiday!
npc.dialogs.Pamela_3: <%s> Do you need any common cooking ingredients?  I have plenty for sale!
npc.dialogs.Parlan_0: <%s> Hello %s, I've got some new plumbing materials restocked today.
npc.dialogs.Parlan_1: <%s> Need to repair your kitchen or bathroom? All my wares are of highest quality!
npc.dialogs.Pingu_0: <%s> You should really check out Sky Penguin’s latest release! Skye and I worked really hard on it.
npc.dialogs.Pingu_1: <%s> I wonder if we will be able to collab with Harley again soon?
npc.dialogs.Ren_1: <%s> Take good care of your tools
npc.dialogs.Rigg_0: <%s> You won't find this raccoon munching on miles tickets, no siree!
npc.dialogs.Rigg_1: <%s> Enchantment books, materials and collectibles, I got it all right here!
npc.dialogs.Sam_0: <%s> Ah, my fishing friend, do you need any equipment?  I hope my supplies can provide what you are seeking.
npc.dialogs.Sam_1: <%s> I must say it is quite refreshing to sell sushi in this area. The people here truly appreciate the taste of quality fish!
npc.dialogs.Sam_2: <%s> Have you caught anything interesting while fishing lately?
npc.dialogs.Skye_0: <%s> Hi %s, you got to check out these latest electronic releases!
npc.dialogs.Skye_1: <%s> I think your office station could use an upgrade!
npc.dialogs.Skye_2: <%s> I just found a new supplier for amps, it's going to be very useful for our next Sky Penguin performance!
npc.dialogs.Yukkie_0: <%s> Do you have any fruits on'ya?
npc.dialogs.Yukkie_1: <%s> Best thing to have after a long day of adventuring is FRUIT!
npcs.catalog.catalogDialog: <%s> Let me find the items I have in storage that matches the items in your inventory...
npcs.fullSettlement.dialog: <%s> Thank you so much for helping all of us move into the settlement! I would be happy to give you a discount!

description.milesTicket.2: - After you have moved in Sam you can sell fishes to him by right clicking him with a fish or a fish satchel with fishes in it
description.milesTicket.3: - To move in Sam catch 5 unique fishes and move in Jess
description.milesTicket.5: - You can earn tickets by cooking dishes for the villagers!
description.milesTicket.6: - cook 5 unique dishes and follow the quests to start making your menu!
description.milesTicket.8: - You can earn tickets by collecting various items in the game!
description.milesTicket.9: - When you complete certain quests you sometimes can unlock collections to complete.  The more items you complete in the collection, the more tickets you will receive as a reward!
description.milesTicket.10: - The collections will be listed in the 'Collection Quests' chapter group and the collection rewards will be in the 'Collection Achievements' chapter
description.milesTicket.11: - Whenever you have a lot of achievements completed, you can collect the ticket rewards from all of them at the same time by clicking the 'Click to collect all rewards!' button on the top right corner (looks like a bag with an exclamation mark over it)
